{"tid":2147746,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★2港人持BNO抵英　被迫申請庇護","createTime":"2020-08-09T12:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T13:42:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"18c4c7f979a7e6805a6656a16495edbc89fb10ce","tid":2147746,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒上周五（7日）報道，有2名港人早前持英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）入境英國時，分別被入境人員要求申請庇護，否則遣返他們。二人被迫申請庇護，而且不獲准按現行政策在英國逗留最多6個月。內政部接獲傳媒查詢後，已更新相關指引。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200809/bkn-20200809123205817-0809_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200809%2Fbkn-20200809123205817-0809_00822_001.html&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminHejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=75d3d0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200809/bkn-20200809123205817-0809_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"38e75e151dd9f93d1fa23a55097520768a72fd2e","tid":2147746,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc23e935fb8f51697741cfa62dee0c9f1d0a6ec2","tid":2147746,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:34:45.000Z","msg":"《每日郵報》指，其中一名港人是任職銷售經理的34歲男子，他上月15日抵達倫敦機場過海關時，關員給他一張滿是方格和文字的細紙張，指他除非申請庇護，否則不能入境。男子懇求關員協助他，若被遣返回港會面臨即時危險，港府或視他逃離是不忠誠，甚至會拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n另一名32歲港人男子則於英國在上月1日公布有關BNO居留事宜後7日，便乘飛機到英國，入境人員同樣要求他申請庇護，否則遣返。他聲稱，其祖父是國民黨特工，他曾與一個外國情報機構分享其祖父管